description: Your favorite boof squad is back together for a reunion! Shannon and AG chat about where they are now and how the last year has been full of unexpected, yet wonderful, plot twists. The girls are growing up AG is officially a Florida mermaid gurliepop and living her best life. She also shares a surprise celebration and announcement! American girl dolls, dolphin assisted births, ambulance rides, they talk about it all in episode 32.
